text: "Unhealthy" is a 2023 song by Anne-Marie featuring Shania Twain and is the title track to her third studio album of the same name. It went to number 19 in the United Kingdom, number 10 in Ireland and Poland, number 5 in the Netherlands and number 9 in Croatia. It is the first top 20 for Shania Twain since December 2004. == References == Category:2023 songs Category:Country pop songs Category:Anne-Marie (singer) songs Category:Shania Twain songs
